Author: supahfly_remix
Content:
People are complaining about the format (hundreds of pages of PDF). Surely one of you talented programmers can create a webapp based on this, and it might even be the genesis of a startup (e.g., traveler's hub for aircraft safety, etc.)

I myself am just interested in reading the damn thing and am too lazy to write scripts to parse it.
